{
  "texts": [
    "The only language combination where GPT-4 and GT were not tied was from English into Turkish.",
    "HE results suggested that GT was clearly the best performing MT system both in adequacy and fluency.",
    "This result may have happened because GPT-4 may contain less Turkish data within its training parameters.",
    "As both systems are proprietary, we cannot fully find the actual reason for this result.",
    "By following this explanation, it is interesting that Catalan -the other low-resourced language -obtained similar results both for GPT-4 and GT."
  ]
}